name: sella
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "sella" %}
{% set version = "2.1.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/Sella-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: dfe262042c87d90fbb69252e9559f53faa52b0c2f41404cf991910d1429c784d

build:
  number: 1
  skip: true  # [win]
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}
  host:
    - cython
    - numpy
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - ase >=3.18.0
    - jax >=0.2.3
    - jaxlib >=0.1.56
    - {{ pin_compatible('numpy') }}
    - python
    - scipy >=1.1.0

test:
  imports:
    - sella
  commands:
    - python -m pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://pypi.org/project/Sella/
  doc_url: https://github.com/zadorlab/sella/wiki
  summary: |
    Sella is a utility for finding first order saddle points
  license: LGPL-3.0-only
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - awvwgk
